### Equations

#### Heuristic Function
\[ f(n) = g(n) + h(n) \]
- \( g(n) \): Cost from the start node to node \( n \).
- \( h(n) \): Heuristic estimate of the cost from node \( n \) to the goal.

#### Weighted A* Algorithm
\[ f(n) = g(n) + w \cdot h(n) \]
- \( w \): Weight factor.

#### Lower Bound Calculation for TSP
\[ \text{Lower Bound} = \sum_{\text{min edges}} \]

#### Alpha-Beta Pruning
\[ \text{Alpha-Cut: } \text{eval(child)} \leq \text{Alpha} \]
\[ \text{Beta-Cut: } \text{Beta} \leq \text{eval(child)} \]

